description:
In this very special episode of Everything Iconic, Danny breaks down Bravo's Summer House. Bravo superfan (and friend) Whitney Fromholtz stops by to talk season 1 and the premiere of season 2. Danny also chats with Stephen McGee, one of the cast members on the show. If you've never watched Summer House, this is (hopefully) a perfect primer. PS my interview with Stephen starts at 31:55. :)

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
